\subsection{The command table and dispatch}

Like every overlay, \texttt{TWN} reads a command through the engine
[[GET_COMMAND]] (which returns $X = 2\times\text{index}$) and jumps
through a word table, [[CMD_TBL]], by self-modifying the operand of a
[[JSR]]. Most of the 26 commands are no-ops in town and point at the
engine's [[QUERY_MARK]] (the ``Huh?'' beep); the rest are the
town-mode handlers below. Accelerator and Noise reuse the engine's
sound toggles.

<<twn command table>>=
        ORG $8A56
CMD_TBL
        DC.W CMD_MOVE
        DC.W $8A90
        DC.W $8A96
        DC.W $8A9C
        DC.W CMD_PASS
        DC.W SOUND_TOGGLE
        DC.W CMD_ATTACK
        DC.W QUERY_MARK
        DC.W CMD_CAST
        DC.W CMD_DROP
        DC.W QUERY_MARK
        DC.W QUERY_MARK
        DC.W CMD_GET
        DC.W QUERY_MARK
        DC.W CMD_INFORM
        DC.W QUERY_MARK
        DC.W SFX_TOGGLE
        DC.W QUERY_MARK
        DC.W CMD_QUIT
        DC.W CMD_READY
        DC.W CMD_STEAL
        DC.W CMD_TRANSACT
        DC.W CMD_UNLOCK
        DC.W QUERY_MARK
        DC.W QUERY_MARK
        DC.W CMD_ZTATS
@

<<twn move>>=
        ORG $8A8A
CMD_MOVE
        SUBROUTINE
        ; The four movement commands and the Pass turn.
        ;
        ; Inputs:
        ;   X = 2*command (0..3); the load below picks the step vector.
        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   Add the step to (ZP_X,ZP_Y); CELL_PROBE the target.  Walking
        ;   off the 38x18 edge (ZP_TX>=$26 or ZP_TY>=$12) leaves town via
        ;   EXIT_TO_OUT.  A blocked cell prints "Blocked"; an open one
        ;   erases the old @ and redraws it at the new cell.  Every move
        ;   (and Pass) spends a turn through TICK_SND.
        ;
        ; Clobbers: A, X, Y
        LDX #$00
        LDY #$FF
        BNE .L8AA0
        LDX #$00
        LDY #$01
        BNE .L8AA0
        LDX #$01
        LDY #$00
        BEQ .L8AA0
        LDX #$FF
        LDY #$00
.L8AA0
        TXA
        CLC
        ADC ZP_X
        STA ZP_TX
        TAX
        TYA
        CLC
        ADC ZP_Y
        STA ZP_TY
        TAY
        JSR CELL_PROBE
        BCS .L8AD8
        LDA ZP_TX
        CMP #$26
        BCS .L8ABF
        LDA ZP_TY
        CMP #$12
        BCC .L8AC2
.L8ABF
        JMP EXIT_TO_OUT
.L8AC2
        LDA #$0E
        JSR SFX_PLAY
        JSR CURSOR_COL1
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "Blocked",0
        JMP CMD_PASS
.L8AD8
        LDX ZP_X
        LDY ZP_Y
        LDA #$20
        JSR PLOT_GLYPH
        LDX ZP_TX
        STX ZP_X
        LDY ZP_TY
        STY ZP_Y
        LDA #$7B
        JSR PLOT_GLYPH
CMD_PASS
        LDY #$01
        LDA #$10
        JSR TICK_SND
.L8AF5
        JSR SFX_DRAIN
        BNE .L8AF5
        RTS
@

<<twn attack>>=
