<<twn drop>>=
        ORG $8CBE
CMD_DROP
        SUBROUTINE
        ; The Drop command front end: Pence, Weapon, or Armour.
        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   Read one of P/W/A, echo the matching prompt from DROP_PROMPTS,
        ;   and RTS-dispatch through DROP_DISP to the chosen sub-handler.
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B " Pence,Weapon,Armour: ",0
        JSR KEY_IDLE
        LDX #$06
        STX MON_CH
        LDX #$03
.L8CE1
        CMP $8CFE,X
        BEQ .L8CE9
        DEX
        BNE .L8CE1
.L8CE9
        TXA
        ASL
        TAY
        LDA DROP_DISP+1,Y
        PHA
        LDA DROP_DISP,Y
        PHA
        JSR STR_NTH
        DC.W DROP_PROMPTS
        JSR CLR_EOL
        INC MON_CH
        RTS
@

The Drop front end matches the typed letter against the three-byte
selector ``PWA'' and RTS-dispatches through [[DROP_DISP]], a table of
\emph{return addresses} (target $-1$) pushed onto the stack.

<<twn drop dispatch>>=
        ORG $8CFF
DROP_SEL
        DC.B "PWA"               ; Drop sub-command letters
DROP_DISP ; RTS-dispatch (target-1), indexed by 2*letter:
        DC.W DROP_SEL-2          ;   Y=0 slot (unused)
        DC.W DROP_PENCE-1        ;   P: drop gold
        DC.W DROP_WEAPON-1       ;   W: drop a weapon
        DC.W DROP_ARMOUR-1       ;   A: drop armour
@

<<twn drop pence>>=
        ORG $8D0A
DROP_PENCE
        SUBROUTINE
        ; Drop Pence: give gold to the person on the player tile.
        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   Read an amount (NUM_INPUT), deduct it from PLR_COIN.  If the
        ;   tile holds the special benefactor NPC (type $61 from NPC_AT),
        ;   the gift returns 1.5x its value as hit points and a random
        ;   spell ("Shazam!" / "Alakazot!"); otherwise just "Ok!".
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "~How much? ",0
        JSR NUM_INPUT
        LDA AMOUNT
        ORA AMOUNT+1
        BNE .L8D25
        RTS
.L8D25
        LDA PLR_COIN
        CMP AMOUNT
        LDA PLR_COIN+1
        SBC AMOUNT+1
        BCS .L8D53
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "~Thou hast not that much!",0
        JMP BEEP_HUH
.L8D53
        LDA PLR_COIN
        SEC
        SBC AMOUNT
        STA PLR_COIN
        LDA PLR_COIN+1
        SBC AMOUNT+1
        STA PLR_COIN+1
        LDX ZP_X
        LDY ZP_Y
        JSR NPC_AT
        CMP #$61
        BEQ .L8D7A
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "~Ok!",0
        RTS
.L8D7A
        LDA AMOUNT
        STA ZP_T0
        LDA AMOUNT+1
        LSR
        STA ZP_T1
        ROR ZP_T0
        LDA ZP_T0
        CLC
        ADC AMOUNT
        STA ZP_T0
        LDA ZP_T1
        ADC AMOUNT+1
        STA ZP_T1
        LDA PLR_HITS
        CLC
        ADC ZP_T0
        STA PLR_HITS
        LDA PLR_HITS+1
        ADC ZP_T1
        STA PLR_HITS+1
        LDA PLR_HITS
        CMP #$0F
        LDA PLR_HITS+1
        SBC #$27
        BCC .L8DBD
        LDA #$0F
        STA PLR_HITS
        LDA #$27
        STA PLR_HITS+1
.L8DBD
        JSR RND
        CMP #$10
        BCC .L8DD5
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "~Shazam!",0
        LDA #$0A
        JMP SFX_PLAY
.L8DD5
        JSR RND
        AND #$0F
        CMP #$08
        BCS .L8DD5
        CMP #$03
        BEQ .L8DD5
        TAX
        INX
        INC OWNED_SPELLS,X
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "~Alakazot!",0
        LDA #$0A
        JMP SFX_PLAY
DROP_WEAPON
        JSR DROP_PICK
        DC.B $0F
        DC.B $83
        ROR STR_WEAPONS,X
        BMI .L8E12
        TAX
        LDA #$00
        STA OWNED_WEAPONS,X
        CPX READY_WEAPON
        BNE .L8E12
        STA READY_WEAPON
.L8E12
        JMP MAP_DRAW
DROP_ARMOUR
        JSR DROP_PICK
        ORA $7D
        ROR STR_ARMOUR,X
        BMI .L8E12
        TAX
        LDA #$00
        STA OWNED_ARMOUR,X
        CPX READY_ARMOUR
        BNE .L8E12
        STA READY_ARMOUR
        JMP MAP_DRAW
CAP_FOOD
        LDA PLR_FOOD
        CMP #$0F
        LDA PLR_FOOD+1
        SBC #$27
        BCC .L8E46
        LDA #$0F
        STA PLR_FOOD
        LDA #$27
        STA PLR_FOOD+1
.L8E46
        RTS
CAP_COIN
        LDA PLR_COIN
        CMP #$0F
        LDA PLR_COIN+1
        SBC #$27
        BCC .L8E5D
        LDA #$0F
        STA PLR_COIN
        LDA #$27
        STA PLR_COIN+1
.L8E5D
        RTS
@

