        DC.B $00,$00                    ; banked kill experience,
                                        ;   doubled into hit
                                        ;   points on exit
KILL_SLOT
        DC.B $00                        ; last kill's slot
BOX_XFL DC.B $00                        ; coffin/chest box corner
BOX_XNL DC.B $00                        ;   coordinates (renderer
BOX_XNR DC.B $00                        ;   workspace; named in
